      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the zenith of naturally aspirated engineering, powered by the iconic S54 inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned dual-VANOS system. This specimen is mechanically flawless, paired with a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory variable M differential lock for surgical power delivery. The chassis integrity is absolute, featuring documented subframe reinforcement and a fully refreshed suspension geometry utilizing OEM components to maintain original kinematics. Every system, from the high-pressure VANOS lines to the cooling system\u2019s thermal management, has been meticulously maintained to ensure peak performance. This is a synchronized, collector-grade masterpiece with zero deferred maintenance, offering an unrivaled tactile driving experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
