      "description": "Presenting an absolute gem: a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with absolutely no chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the premium leather remains supple and scent-free, with every electronic feature and tactile button functioning with factory precision. This car has been meticulously garage-kept in a climate-controlled environment and serviced exclusively at authorized dealerships, accompanied by a complete, organized folder of all maintenance records. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach\u2014the engine is whisper-quiet, the transmission shifts are seamless, and there are zero leaks or undercarriage wear. If you are looking for a showroom-quality example that has been pampered since day one, this is the definitive choice for your collection.",
